ent-Z14STWeaponSMGMP5Celebra = H&K MP-5 "Celebra"
    .desc = Custom MP-5 variant with distinctive Poisk faction markings. Features unique blue finish while maintaining all the reliability of the original design. It uses 9x19mm ammo.
    .suffix = Z14

ent-Z14STWeaponSMGVector9 = KRISS Vector 9mm
    .desc = Next-generation submachine gun with unique delayed blowback system delivering exceptional controllability during high-rate fire. Chambered in 9x19mm Parabellum.
    .suffix = Z14

ent-Z14STWeaponSMGVector9Black = KRISS Vector 9mm (Black)
    .desc = Tactical black variant maintaining all advanced recoil mitigation features in sleek low-visibility package.
    .suffix = Z14

ent-Z14STWeaponSMGVector9Forest = KRISS Vector 9mm (Forest Camo)
